captions_en: A back side view of a yellow van on the road in the countryside under blue sky.

captions_en: A pepperoni pizza on a white plate on a wooden plate.

captions_en: A side view of a wooden pier on the lake surrounded by trees.

captions_en: A macro shot of a cup of tea placed on a table.

captions_en: Green woods in a thickset forest with sunlight in background.

captions_en: A black address board on a brick textured wall.

captions_en: Several young people protesting at a place for the Syrian revolution with a background of a destroyed building.

captions_en: An aerial view of two cities divided by a river.
